PROJECT STOCKERRR ..

The Idea: Make a practise US stock trading app using MEAN stack

The Flow Decided till now: 1. user registration sign up login

2. user get certain amount in wallet balance to spend on stocks

3. user can liquedate money when they want

4. use alpaca API for tis

5. dont actually have to buy the asset from alpaca, u can jst create and order, remember the price for which it was bought for, create a transaction and proceed accordingly.

6. 


